{"tid":512364,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「iPhone 變慢案」集體訴訟　要求蘋果賠 9990 億美元","createTime":"2017-12-28T11:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-28T13:56:55.000Z","uid":141060,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1170960e8a94450ea451d48748b08d0c238edc19","tid":512364,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"蘋果早前承認在 iOS 升級中，加入電池變舊手機的處理器速度限制，令一些購買了已有兩年或以上的舊機，出現效能下降的情況。雖然蘋果指這種做法是避免手機自動關機的情況出現，但有 iPhone 用戶就準備在美國展開集體訴訟，要求蘋果賠償的金額達到 9990 億美元（約7.8萬億港元）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/iFixit-iPhone-6s-teardown-image-004-Battery-694x521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FiFixit-iPhone-6s-teardown-image-004-Battery-694x521.jpg&h=4f3e556c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據 iDownloadblog 的報道，「蘋果雖然以保護內置劣化電池的手機作為理由，但此政策有引誘用戶購買新 iPhone 之目的」為理由，一個消費者團體開始展開集體訴訟。原告一方要求的賠償總額為 9990 億美元。<br />\n<br />\n文件網址：<a href=\"https://zh.scribd.com/document/367854131/Violetta-Mailyan-vs-Apple-Class-Action-of-Purposely-Slowing-IPhones\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F367854131%2FVioletta-Mailyan-vs-Apple-Class-Action-of-Purposely-Slowing-IPhones&d=8Eiy3MSIFy3n6AHnM7FkejPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6e2029a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.scribd.com/document/367854131/Violetta-Mailyan-vs-Apple-Class-Action-of-Purposely-Slowing-IPhones</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2017-12-28-17.24.50-694x521.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2017-12-28-17.24.50-694x521.png&h=dbce8b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現時原告一方的訴狀在網路上亦可閱覽。iDownloadblog 指今次引起集體訴訟的原因，是蘋果多年來也沒有對顧客透露會把舊機降低效能的事實，指蘋果解釋他們並非意圖令 iPhone 再不能使用，但要用戶接受這個解釋恐怕有點困難。而蘋果有意圖令舊機效能降低是一個事實，他們需要負上相關責任。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：iDownloadblog<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82f894c4ea4e96c91557b0cf7e4cddc9ba402f9","tid":512364,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"屈完佢賠又買下一代IPHONE <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69a22f5222d78eba29da957c4990f3c8ecf8915","tid":512364,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d02d0647b5a3e6fc2f0f40fd82cbf2858449205","tid":512364,"uid":28714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"賠完咪將iPhone再加價<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0e6e547e7ac7ac32276069cf9cc427081c6e8d","tid":512364,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T12:52:21.000Z","msg":"下年又可以加多d價繼續測試fans忠誠度<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f82dd9ed55dd3d051967d05269d8263f1f4da543","tid":512364,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"賠9990億<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果市值先9000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f827a0d78aacc6d36a83d3f7ff981ff7d53542b","tid":512364,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f82dd9ed55dd3d051967d05269d8263f1f4da543","tid":512364,"uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:54:17.000Z","msg":"賠9990億<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果市值先9000億<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"直接收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3cb9edecfe365d61fe94448bdc425654bed01a","tid":512364,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"告到蘋果破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}